OL,3,C'I constantly look over my shoulder' -
OL,4,Cyoung rape victim sees attacker jailed
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man who raped a teenager
OL,7,Fand sexually abused an underage girl
OL,8,Fin Bristol has been jailed.
OL,10,FKaydon Hall has been sentenced to
OL,11,Fseven years and two months in prison
OL,12,Fat Bristol Crown Court on Friday 22
OL,13,FMarch after committing crimes
OL,14,Fdescribed by police as "horrific" and
OL,15,F"sickening".
OL,17,FHall, who is of no fixed address,
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to the rape of a girl
OL,19,Fover the age of 16, as well as two
OL,20,Fcounts of engaging in sexual activity
OL,21,Fwith a teenager under the age of 16.
