OL,6,FShe added it felt like her life 'had
OL,7,Fbeen put on hold' while the police
OL,8,Finvestigation and court proceedings
OL,9,Ftook place.
OL,11,FHall's second victim, told the court:
OL,12,F"What happened to me still remains at
OL,13,Fthe forefront of my mind. I cannot
OL,14,Fescape it.
OL,16,F"I want to be able to forget it and
OL,17,Fmove on but I can't.
