OL,3,C'I constantly look over my shoulder' -
OL,4,Cyoung rape victim sees attacker jailed
OL,6,F"It enters my mind several times of
OL,7,Fthe day, there is no rhyme or reason
OL,8,Fto this. When it does, it makes me
OL,9,Ffeel uncomfortable in my own skin and
OL,10,Fnauseous."
OL,12,FDuring sentencing, Her Honour Judge
OL,13,FMoira Macmillan told Hall that his
OL,14,Foffending has had a huge impact on the
OL,15,Fvictims' lives and their mental health.
