OL,4,Cyoung rape victim sees attacker jailed
OL,6,FHall, in addition to his prison
OL,7,Fsentence, was made subject of
OL,8,Findefinite sexual harm prevention
OL,9,Forder and restraining order. He will
OL,10,Falso be on the sexual offenders'
OL,11,Fregister for life.
OL,13,FDetective Constable Hannah Pinnell,
OL,14,Fofficer in the case, said: "The
OL,15,Fextraordinary courage of these two
OL,16,Fyoung victims to report what happened
OL,17,Fto them and supporting the legal
OL,18,Fprocess cannot be understated.
