OL,6,F"While the mental impact of what they
OL,7,Fwere subjected to continues to affect
OL,8,Ftheir day-to-day lives, I hope in time
OL,9,Fthey take great pride in what they
OL,10,Fhave done in helping to bring this
OL,11,Fsexual predator before the courts.
OL,13,F"Without their bravery Kaydon Hall
OL,14,Fcould still pose a danger to girls and
OL,15,Fwomen.
