OL,3,C'I constantly look over my shoulder' -
OL,4,Cyoung rape victim sees attacker jailed
OL,6,F"Hall's horrific crimes are sickening.
OL,7,FHe lied through his police interviews
OL,8,Fin an attempt to avoid being brought
OL,9,Fto justice and we welcome the prison
OL,10,Fsentence he has received which will
OL,11,Fhelp keep the public safe.
OL,13,F"We'd encourage anyone who has been a
OL,14,Fvictim of a sexual offence to please
OL,15,Freport it to us ` you will be
OL,16,Fbelieved, we will investigate
OL,17,Fthoroughly and will do whatever we can
OL,18,Fto secure a conviction."
